es.utils.mapper.factory.builder

Interface From<IN,OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    IN - the type of the origin object
    OUT - the type of the destination object
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EMBuilder

    public interface From<IN,OUT>
    First step of the EMBuilder that manage the creation of the getter operation.
    This step is mandatory Next step: DefaultInput
    Author:
    eschoysman
    See Also:
    ClassMapper.addMapping(), EMBuilder.using(Mapper,ClassMapper), ElementMapper, builder package
